        <div xml:id="d1e277" type="textpart" subtype="part" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
          <div xml:id="d1e279" type="textpart" subtype="case" n="C.4" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <head>(C.4)</head>
            <div xml:id="d1e284" type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 d.init." part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
              <head>(C.4 d.init.)</head>
              <ab part="N">
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">Quidam</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P"/>
                </app>
                in
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">excommunicatione</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">excomunicatione</rdg>
                </app>
                constitutus episcopum accusare disponit;
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #P">adolescentem</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Bc">adulescentem</rdg>
                </app>
                infra xiiiium
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Bc #P">etatis sue annum</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Aa">annum etatis sue</rdg>
                </app>
                ad assertionem sue cause adducit. Prohibitus ab accusatione
                adolescentem accusatorem et se testem facit. Adolescens personam
                accusatoris et testis gerere cupit;
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">die</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">di</rdg>
                </app>
                statuta ad
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #P">iudicium</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditium</rdg>
                </app>
                electorum
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">iudicum</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">iudicium</rdg>
                </app>
                episcopus minime
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc #P">concurrit</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Fr.">occurrit</rdg>
                </app>;
                a communione
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">suspenditur</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">suspendere</rdg>
                </app>;
                tandem renouato
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #P">iudicio</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                </app>
                accusator culpabilis in accusatione
                inuenitur; demum ad assertionem proprie cause procedit. Hic primum
                queritur, an in excommunicatione constitutus alium accusare ualeat?
                Secundo,
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">an</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">autem</rdg>
                </app>
                infra
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc"/>
                  <rdg wit="#P">infra</rdg>
                </app>
                xiiiium annum in
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">criminali</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">criminari</rdg>
                </app>
                causa testari quis possit? Tercio, utrum
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">ab</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P"/>
                </app>
                accusatione prohibitus personam testificantis possit assumere?
                Quarto,
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">an idem possit esse accusator et testis? Quinto,</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P"/>
                </app>
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">an</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#P">aut</rdg>
                </app>
                die constituta non occurrens a communione sit remouendus? Sexto, si
                in episcoporum
                <app>
                  <lem wit="#Aa #P">iudicio</lem>
                  <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                </app>
                accusatoris persona culpabilis inuenta
                fuerit, an ad assertionem proprie cause de cetero sit admittenda?
              </ab>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="d1e444" type="textpart" subtype="question" n="C.4 q.1" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
              <head>(C.4 q.1)</head>
              <div xml:id="d1e449" type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.1 d.a.c.1" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.1 d.a.c.1)</head>
                <ab part="N">
                  De prima questione sic statutum legitur in
                  <app>
                    <lem wit="#Aa #P">concilio</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#Bc">comcilio</rdg>
                  </app>
                  Cartaginensi .vii. cui interfuit Faustinus Romane ecclesie legatus:
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div xml:id="d1e467" type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.1 c.1" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.1 c.1)</head>
                <div xml:id="d1e472" type="textpart" subtype="rubric" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Ad accusandum non
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">admittitur</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">admittatur</rdg>
                    </app>
                    qui in excommunicatione perseuerat.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e487" type="textpart" subtype="canon" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <!--
                    Clavis Canonum search for
                    Incipit = 'definimus eum rite ad accusationem non' and
                    Explicit = 'voluerit accusare laicus'
                    (matches Aa, Bc) returns 7 results:
                    AE03.117, CA05.077, DR02.32.126, ID14.069,
                    LP0647, PX05.01.51, and RM222.

                    Clavis Canonum search for
                    Incipit = 'definimus eum rite ad accusationem non' and
                    Explicit = 'voluerit accusare clericus'
                    (matches P) returns 1 result:
                    DS06.01.080
                  -->
                  <ab part="N">
                    Diffinimus, eum rite ad accusationem non admitti, qui
                    posteaquam excommunicatus
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">fuerit</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">fuit</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    in ipsa adhuc excommunicatione constitutus, siue sit
                    clericus
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">siue laicus</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P"/>
                    </app>,
                    accusare uoluerit. Omnes etiam infamie maculis aspersi, id
                    est
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">istriones</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">hystriones</rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#Fr.">histriones</rdg>
                    </app>
                    aut turpitudinibus subiecte persone, heretici etiam, siue
                    pagani siue Iudei, ab accusatione prohibentur.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="d1e526" type="textpart" subtype="question" n="C.4 q.2-3" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
              <head>(C.4 q.2-3)</head>
              <div xml:id="d1e531" type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.2-3 d.a.c.1" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.2-3 d.a.c.1)</head>
                <ab part="N">
                  Secunda autem et
                  <app>
                    <lem wit="#Aa #Bc #P">tercia</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#Fr.">tertia</rdg>
                  </app>
                  questio eodem concilio, uno eodemque capitulo
                  <app>
                    <lem wit="#Bc #P">terminatur</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#Aa">terminantur</rdg>
                  </app>.
                  Illud uero est huiusmodi:
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div xml:id="d1e558" type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.2-3 c.1" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.2-3 c.1)</head>
                <div xml:id="d1e563" type="textpart" subtype="rubric" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Qui ab accusatione repelluntur,
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#P #Fr.">aut</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">et</rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc"/>
                    </app>
                    ad annum .xiiii. nondum peruenerunt, testes esse non possunt.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e580" type="textpart" subtype="canon" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Testes autem ad testimonium
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">non</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P"/>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">admittendos</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">admttendos</rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#Fr.">admittendos esse</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <!-- esse add. Fr.
                      <app>
                        <lem wit="#Aa #Bc #P"/>
                        <rdg wit="#Fr.">esse</rdg>
                      </app>
                    -->
                    censemus, qui nec ad accusationem admitti iussi sunt, uel
                    etiam quos ipse accusator de domo sua produxerit. Ad
                    testimonium autem
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">intra</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">infra</rdg>
                    </app>
                    annos .xiiii. etatis sue constituti non admittantur.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e617" type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.2-3 d.p.c.3" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <head>(C.4 q.2-3 d.p.c.3)</head>
                  <!-- "Set" or "Sed"? S; in Aa and P, S⁊ in Bc. -->
                  <ab part="N">
                    Set obicitur illud beati
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">Bricii</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">Brichi</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    qui uoce pueri .xxx. dies ab
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">ortu</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">hortu</rdg>
                    </app>
                    habentis innocens probatus est. Set miracula diuina sunt
                    admiranda, non in exemplum humane
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">actionis</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">accionis</rdg>
                    </app>
                    trahenda.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="d1e657" type="textpart" subtype="question" n="C.4 q.4" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
              <head>(C.4 q.4)</head>
              <div xml:id="d1e662" type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.4 d.a.c.1" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.4 d.a.c.1)</head>
                <ab part="N">
                  De
                  <app>
                    <lem wit="#Bc #P">quarta</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#Aa">.iiii.</rdg>
                  </app>
                  uero questione Fabianus papa constituit, dicens:
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div xml:id="d1e680" type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.4 c.1" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.4 c.1)</head>
                <div xml:id="d1e685" type="textpart" subtype="rubric" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">Accusator, testis uel iudex aliquis simul esse non potest.</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">Quilibet duas personas in causa <sic>gegrere</sic> non ualet.</rdg>
                    </app>
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e703" type="textpart" subtype="canon" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Nullus umquam presumat accusator simul esse et iudex uel testis, quoniam in omni
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">iudicio</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <lem>quatuor</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">iiii</rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">iiii<add place="above" instant="false" status="unremarkable">o</add></rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#P">iiii<add place="above" instant="false" status="unremarkable">or</add></rdg>
                    </app> personas semper
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc #P">necesse est esse</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Fr.">esse necesse est</rdg>
                    </app>, id
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">est</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P"/>
                    </app>
                    iudices electos, et
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">accusatores</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa"><add place="above" instant="false" status="unremarkable">idoneos</add>accusatores</rdg>
                    </app>, ac
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">defensores</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">defensores<add place="above" instant="false" status="unremarkable">congruos</add></rdg>
                    </app> atque
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">testes</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa"><add place="above" instant="false" status="unremarkable">legitimos</add>testes</rdg>
                    </app>.
                  </ab>
                  <!-- Aa only, possible later addition, foot of 149v -->
                  <ab part="N">
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa">
                      Iudices
                      <expan instant="false">aut<ex instant="false">em</ex></expan>
                      debent uti
                      <expan instant="false">eq<ex instant="false">ui</ex>tate</expan>,
                      testes
                      <expan instant="false">u<ex instant="false">er</ex>itate</expan>,
                      accusatores
                      <!-- nested <app> element -->
                      <app>
                        <lem wit="#Aa" xml:id="lem-intentione">intentione</lem>
                        <witDetail wit="#Aa" target="#lem-intentione" type="correction-original"/>
                        <rdg wit="#Aa" xml:id="rdg-intensione">intensione</rdg>
                        <witDetail wit="#Aa" target="#lem-intensione" type="correction-altered"/>
                      </app>
                      ad
                      <expan instant="false">amplificanda<ex instant="false">m</ex></expan>
                      <expan instant="false">causa<ex instant="false">m</ex></expan>,
                      defensores extenuatione ad
                      <expan instant="false">minuenda<ex instant="false">m</ex></expan>
                      <expan instant="false">causa<ex instant="false">m</ex></expan>.
                      </lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc #P"/>
                    </app>
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div xml:id="d1e855" type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.4 c.2" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.4 c.2)</head>
                <div xml:id="d1e860" type="textpart" subtype="inscription" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">Item Damasus papa.</ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e866" type="textpart" subtype="rubric" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">Quilibet in causa duas personas gerere non ualet.</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">Accusator, testis uel iudex aliquis simul esse non potest.</rdg>
                    </app>
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e881" type="textpart" subtype="canon" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Nullus introducatur personaliter
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">ad causam</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">adusam</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    <!-- "sed" or "set"? ſ; in Aa and P, ſ⁊ in Bc. -->
                    set accusatores et accusati equa audiantur ratione, iuxta
                    quod ordo exigit. Accusatores uero et iudices non
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc #P">idem</lem>
                      <!--
                        "iidem" Fr. 541
                        "idem" Ka 112rb and Kb 115rb
                      -->
                      <rdg wit="#Fr.">iidem</rdg>
                    </app>
                    sint, set
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">per se accusatores,</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P"/>
                    </app>
                    per se iudices, per
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">se</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">re</rdg>
                    </app>
                    testes, per se accusati, unusquisque
                    in suo ordine. Inscriptio
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P"/>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">uero</rdg>
                    </app>
                    semper fiat ut
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">talionem calumpniator</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">calumpniator talionem</rdg>
                    </app>
                    recipiat, quia ante inscriptionem nemo debet iudicari uel
                    dampnari, cum et seculi leges hec eadem retineant.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="d1e947" type="textpart" subtype="question" n="C.4 q.5" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
              <head>(C.4 q.5)</head>
              <div xml:id="d1e952" type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.5 d.a.c.1" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.5 d.a.c.1)</head>
                <ab part="N">
                  De .v. uero questione in concilio cartaginensi
                  <app>
                    <lem wit="#Bc">tertio</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#Aa">.iii.</rdg>
                    <rdg wit="#P">tercio</rdg>
                  </app>
                  sic
                  <app>
                    <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">inuenitur</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#P"><sic>inueuenitur</sic></rdg>
                  </app>
                  diffinitum.
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div xml:id="d1e983" type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.5 c.1" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.5 c.1)</head>
                <div xml:id="d1e988" type="textpart" subtype="rubric" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Non est a communione suspendendus, qui die statuta ad causam
                    peruenire non potuit.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e994" type="textpart" subtype="canon" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Quisquis episcoporum accusatur, ad primates
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">prouincie</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">prouintie</rdg>
                    </app>
                    ipsius causam deferat accusator. Nec a communione
                    suspendatur cui crimen intenditur, nisi ad causam suam
                    dicendam electorum
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">iudicum</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">iudicium</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    die statuta,
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">litteris</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">litteras</rdg>
                    </app>
                    euocatus minime occurrerit, hoc est
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc">infra spatium</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">intra spacium</rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#P">infra infra spatium</rdg>
                    </app>
                    mensis ex ea die, qua eum litteras accepisse constiterit.
                    Quod si aliquas ueras necessitatis causas
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">probauerit</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">propriauerit</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    quibus occurrere non potuisse manifestum sit,
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc #P">cause sue</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Fr.">sue cause</rdg>
                    </app>
                    dicende intra alterum mensem integram habeat facultatem.
                    Verum tamdiu post mensem secundum non communicet, donec
                    purgetur. Si autem ad uniuersale concilium
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">anniuersarium</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">anniuersalium</rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#Fr."/>
                    </app>
                    occurrere
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">noluerit</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">uoluerit</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    ut uel ibi causa eius terminetur, ipse in se dampnationis
                    sententiam dixisse iudicetur. Tempore sane, quo non
                    communicat, nec in sua ecclesia uel parrochia communicet.
                    Accusator autem eius, si numquam diebus cause dicende
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">defuerit</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">affuerit</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <!--
                      '^' after "defuerti" in Aa, indicating addition
                      "ſubt[ra]hens ſe" in right margin of 150r.
                    -->
                    <app>
                      <!-- lemma uncertain, check Fd -->
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">non remoueatur a communione. Si uero aliquando defuerit</rdg>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc #P"/>
                    </app>
                    subtrahens se, restituto in
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">communione</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">communionem</rdg>
                    </app>
                    episcopo, remoueatur a communione accusator, ita tamen, ut
                    nec ipsi adimatur facultas cause peragende,
                    <!-- "set" or "sed"? ſ; in Aa and P, ſet in Bc. -->
                    si se ad diem
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P"/>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">constitutam</rdg>
                    </app>
                    non
                    <app>
                      <!-- lemma uncertain, check Fd -->
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P" xml:id="rdg-uoluisse">uoluisse</lem>
                      <witDetail wit="#Aa" target="#rdg-uoluisse" type="correction-original"/>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa #Bc" xml:id="rdg-noluisse">noluisse</rdg>
                      <witDetail wit="#Aa" target="#rdg-noluisse" type="correction-altered"/>
                    </app>
                    set non potuisse occurrere probauerit.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="d1e1136" type="textpart" subtype="question" n="C.4 q.6" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
              <head>(C.4 q.6)</head>
              <div xml:id="d1e1141" type="textpart" subtype="dictum" n="C.4 q.6 d.a.c.1" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.6 d.a.c.1)</head>
                <ab part="N">
                  Sexta uero questio eodem capitulo terminatur, in quo sequitur:
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div xml:id="d1e1150" type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.6 c.1" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.6 c.1)</head>
                <div xml:id="d1e1155" type="textpart" subtype="rubric" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <!--
                    R2: "In ciuili et proprio dumtaxat negotio ad arguendum
                    admittitur, qui in episcopi accusatione culpabilis inuenitur."
                  -->
                  <ab part="N">
                    Qui in accusatione episcopi culpabilis inuenitur ad
                    arguendum de cetero non admittatur nisi propriam causam
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">ciuilem</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P"/>
                    </app>
                    solummodo asserere uoluerit.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e1171" type="textpart" subtype="canon" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Illud uero placuit, ut cum agere ceperit in episcoporum
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">iudicio</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    si fuerit
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">accusatoris</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">accusator</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa">persona</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc #P"/>
                    </app>
                    dampnabilis de cetero ad arguendum non admittatur, nisi
                    proprias causas, non tamen ecclesiasticas uel criminales,
                    asserere uoluerit.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div xml:id="d1e1204" type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.6 c.2" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.6 c.2)</head>
                <div xml:id="d1e1209" type="textpart" subtype="inscription" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Item ex
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">concilio</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">comcilio</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">cartaginensi</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">cartaginesi</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">.vii.</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">.viio.</rdg>
                    </app>
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e1242" type="textpart" subtype="rubric" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <!-- R2: "Propriam causam agere ualet cui accusare non licet." -->
                  <ab part="N">
                    Non
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">negatur</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">negant</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                      <!--
                        <lem wit="#Aa">audientia in</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">audiencia in</rdg>
                      -->
                      <lem wit="#Aa #P">
                        <!-- nested <app> element -->
                        <app>
                          <lem wit="#Aa">audientia</lem>
                          <rdg wit="#P">audiencia</rdg>
                        </app>
                      in
                      </lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">in audientia</rdg>
                    </app>
                    propria causa
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Aa #Bc">cuius</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#P">cui</rdg>
                    </app>
                    accusatio interdicitur.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e1290" type="textpart" subtype="canon" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Omnibus quibus accusatio denegatur in causis propriis
                    accusandi licentia
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc #P">non est</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Aa">est non</rdg>
                    </app>
                    neganda.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- 4.6.3 Bc only -->
              <div xml:id="d1e1309" type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.6 c.3" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.6 c.3)</head>
                <div xml:id="d1e1314" type="textpart" subtype="inscription" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">Item Felix episcopus omnibus episcopis</ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e1320" type="textpart" subtype="rubric" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    In episcoporum accusatione
                    <app>
                      <lem>deficiens</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">defitiens</rdg>
                    </app>,
                    ciuiliter
                    <app>
                      <lem>tantum</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">tatum</rdg>
                    </app>
                    experiri poterit.
                  </ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e1344" type="textpart" subtype="canon" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Si accusatorum persone in
                    <app>
                      <lem>iudicio</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                    </app>
                    episcoporum culpabiles
                    <app>
                      <lem wit="#Bc">apparuerint</lem>
                      <!-- Friedberg typo -->
                      <rdg wit="#Fr."><sic>aparuerint</sic></rdg>
                    </app>,
                    ad arguendum non admittantur, nisi proprias causas asserere,
                    non tamen criminales uel ecclesiasticas, uoluerint.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- 4.6.4 Bc only -->
              <div xml:id="d1e1374" type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="C.4 q.6 c.4" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                <head>(C.4 q.6 c.4)</head>
                <div xml:id="d1e1379" type="textpart" subtype="inscription" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">Item Adrianus papa</ab>
                </div>
                <div xml:id="d1e1385" type="textpart" subtype="canon" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
                  <ab part="N">
                    Quod si accusatorum persone in
                    <app>
                      <lem>iudicio</lem>
                      <rdg wit="#Bc">iuditio</rdg>
                    </app>
                    episcoporum et cetera, ut supra eisdem uerbis.
                  </ab>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
